Package: rockfallveg
Type: Package
Title: A Tool for Quantitative Multitemporal Analysis of NDVI Values and Change in Rockfall Debris Bodies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jakob", "Aschauer", email = "jakob.aschauer@student.uibk.ac.at", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions for importing Sentinel-2 data, computing NDVI, cropping to a region of interest, and producing summary plots for multitemporal vegetation analysis.
